        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks JDH and Lyell for the actions they have taken with respect to ARW’s and CD’s papers. Considers himself fortunate to have been given any merit for his work. Is pleased that his correspondence has led to the earlier publication of CD’s work. It would have caused him "much pain &amp; regret" if CD had made ARW’s paper public unaccompanied by his own views.</p>
        </abstract>
